TITLE: Episode 41 - Winning the War
DESCRIPTION: Jessie finds herself alone in more ways than one.  While Maddie is practicing self-care, Jessie discusses the ongoing misinformation about the Chinese Coronavirus and talks about the real crisis...our loss of freedom.
